parameters:
Eek...!! The Divine Dragon is angry...! This village is done
for...!!

It's okay... It's going to be okay...!! Oh, God...!! Please,
protect this child...!!

\SE[22]Let's clean up quickly! Laura! \SE[19]I'll focus on
making sure there's no damage! \SE[20]Take advantage of the
opportunity and clean up skillfully!

H-Hey... Are we going to be okay...? Leaving it all to those
kids...
Y-Yes! W-We need to escape quickly, everyone...!

\SE[18] (The people are in turmoil... Now is the time! This
timing...!!)

\SE[15] (Hmm, I've received a signal... \SE[14] Well, I
guess there's no other choice...!)

\SE[5]Wait...! That white hair, the mysterious large flower
ornament... Carrying two swords...! \SE[15]Could it be...!

\SE[16]It's been rumored in the city...! \SE[15]There's no
mistake, that is...!!
(Here, take a moment to... gather myself...)

\SE[17]That is... 'Laura of the Zero Moon'...!! \SE[15]She's
a recently popular and talented 'girl swordsman'...!!
Mama? What is 'Laura of the Zero Moon'?

It seems like the child who is rumored in the city! Surely
that child will come to our rescue...!
Amazing!! Do your best!! Go, Laura-chan, go!!!

\SE[18] (Alright, I've created a good atmosphere.
\!\SE[19]Surprisingly, I'm quite skilled at inciting.
\!\SE[23]I'll do it. \.Vita.)
\SE[5]Did... did we manage to do it somehow...?

\SE[17]As expected of 'Laura of the Zero Moon'...!!
\SE[15]She truly has the rumored skills!! \SE[14]I knew
there was something special about her! There's no doubt
she'll become a 'super cool girl swordsman' in the
future...!!

Laura of the Zero Moon... Thanks to that child, we were
saved...!
Thank you, Laura-chan! Keep doing your best!!

\SE[16] (Hehe... Just as I expected. \!\SE[23]If we continue
to spread awareness like this...!)
